						<summary>

						<p>Slab built into the wall of a room on the north side of the central platform inside the <hi rend="italic">prākāra</hi> of the Venkaṭēśvara temple.</p>						

						<p>ŚUBHAKṚIT.</p>						

						<p>This record is dated in the cyclic year, Śubhakṛitu, Vaiśākha śu. 5.</p>						

						<p>Registers the gift of lands containing the Tamarind trees and <hi rend="italic">rēgaḍu</hi> lands for maintaining the worship and offerings to god Venkaṭāḍri of Iñjēḍu by Maṭli Varadarāju.</p>						

